European Stocks Decline for Second Day; Telecom, Insurance Shares Retreat

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-05-13T13:40:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/european-stocks-decline-for-second-day-telecom-insurance-shares-retreat.html
European stocks fell for a second
day, erasing an earlier gain, as telecommunication and insurance
companies declined. The Stoxx Europe 600 Index slipped 0.3
percent to 280.98 at 2:38 p.m. in  London , having earlier risen
as much as 0.5 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
